Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{There are three dorms\Nin Easton Magic Academy.}{\i0}Có 3 kí túc xá ở học viện ma pháp Easton.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Students with corresponding characteristics\Nare assigned to each dorm.}{\i0}Tuỳ theo năng lực mà học sinh được chia theo từng nhà.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Adler. Courage and conviction.}{\i0}Adler. Niềm tin và sự dũng cảm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Orca. Wisdom and willingness.}{\i0}Orca. Tri thức và học hỏi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Lang. Ability and ambition.}{\i0}Lang. Năng lực và tham vọng.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The dorms are rivals with one another.}{\i0}Ba nhà này là đối thủ của nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{To visualize their principles and positions,}{\i0}Để hiểu rõ vai trò và vị trí từng nhà,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.46,0:00:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{their friendly rivalry\Ncarries across the entire academy.}{\i0}học viện đã tổ chức nhiều cuộc cạnh tranh thân thiện.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This is the Adler dorm,\Nwhere Mash and Finn reside.}{\i0}Đây là nhà Adler, nơi Mash và Finn ở.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:13.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{In their room, Room 302...}{\i0}Phòng số 302...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{So, five silver coins make one gold coin?}Vậy được 5 xu bạc là đổi lên 1 xu vàng?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's five minus two. Let's see...}5 trừ 2, xem nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Just 28 left.}Còn 28 đồng nữa nhỉ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Five minus two is three.}5 trừ 2 là 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's a trick question?}Câu hỏi bẫy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{No, there's no tricks about this!}Không không... không ai bẫy mày cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{So I'm a meathead?}Vậy tớ là thằng ngu hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You got that right, but...}Đúng rồi đấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{In any case, it's so peaceful today\Nwith nothing going on.}Cơ mà hôm nay yên bình ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It sure is...}Ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{No, there is something!\NOur assignment!}Không, không! Có đó. Nhiệm vụ!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:49.14,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{ZOOM}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh. Really?}Có à?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Crap, crap, I forgot about it!}Quên mất luôn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{If we don't submit our Potions assignment,}Nếu không nộp báo cáo của môn dược học,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{we'll be severely marked down\Nand we'll be in the drop-out range!}chúng ta sẽ bị đánh rớt đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Want one?}Ăn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{This isn't the time for snacks!}Mày có hiểu tiếng người không đấy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Sorry.}Xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I have to do it! I have to do it!\NI have to do my Potions assignment!}Phải làm thôi! Phải mau chóng làm bài tập!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You still haven't done it yet?}Vẫn chưa xong à?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh, it's the lolicon.}A, thằng lolicon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's siscon to you.}Bố mày Siscon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Loitering around doing nothing...}Hờ hững chẳng thèm quan tâm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You two are the dictionary definition\Nof slackers.}Các ngươi đúng là những tên lười biếng...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Wait, Lance. Did you finish already?}Cậu làm xong rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Of course.\NI'm a lot more conscious than you are.}Dĩ nhiên. Ta khác 2 ngươi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:34.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I should've expected that\Nfrom the top student in our class.}{\i0}Không hổ danh học sinh ưu tú.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Lance is simply flawless.}{\i0}Quá hoàn hảo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Guys like you\Nmight ruin the dorm's reputation.}Đám tụi mày sẽ huỷ hoại danh tiếng của KTX.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Have some shame.}Tự nhục đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:50.96,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{SMASH}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{He flew backwards by himself?}Sao nó lại dính sát thương vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{O, my precious!}{\i0}Em gái...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Foisting thy fair light\Nupon my feeble eyes unwarn’d!}{\i0}Mày dám... sử dụng ánh sáng thần thánh đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{‘Tis my fate to succumb\Nto thy infinite warmth.}{\i0}Số phận của ta... là chịu khuất phục...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}{I love you!}{\i0}Anh yêu em!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You use these for the Potions assignment.}Những gì cần làm cho bài kiểm tra lần này là đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What was with that\Ndramatic display just now?}{\i0}Cái trò khi nãy là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{A mandragora.}Mandragora.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Silence their screams and they become\Na universal ingredient in potions.}Khiến chúng im miệng và trở thành nguyên liệu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:19.36,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{AIEEEEEE!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh, another thing that uses magic.}A, lại một thứ nữa sử dụng ma thuật.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{"Another"? You know\Nthis is magic school, right?}Lại? Tao tưởng đây là trường phép?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'll show you how it's done.}Để ta làm mẫu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Quientus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Làm đi.{You try.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Quientus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Quientus!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I can't do it. It won't stop screaming.}Không được, nó cứ la hoài.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Finn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Your center of gravity is unstable.\NYour core muscles are quite weak.}Trọng tâm của cậu không ổn định. Quá yếu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Huh? Core muscles?}Hả? Trọng tâm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Quientus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I think it's gotten worse?\NIts pupils are dilated, too.}{\i0}Hình như nó... la to hơn khi nãy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Finn, focus your magic\Non a single point.}Finn, tập trung ma lực vào một điểm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh, okay.}À ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Listen up, Finn.}Nghe đây Finn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Visualize gently caressing it\Nas you release the magic.}Hình dung rằng đang vuốt ve nó khi làm phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{O-Okay.}À ừ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Quientus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Slowly. That's it.}Từ từ. Đúng rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I did it! I did it, Lance!}Thành công rồi, Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:41.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Even slackers like you\Nshould be able to do this much.}Ngay cả một đứa lười như ngươi cũng nên làm được.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Thanks!}Cảm ơn cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Maybe Lance is really good\Nat taking care of others.}{\i0}Có khi Lance là một tên tốt bụng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh, yeah. How is Mash doing?}Ủa? Mash đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That plant's flipped out! It's so huge!}{\i0}Sao nó lại như thế này?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:07.47,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{SLAP}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I did it.}Xong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Did you really, though?}Xong cái quái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:20.10,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{MANDRAGORA COOKING}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Once they're asleep,\Nthey turn into a regular herb.}Khi chúng ngủ rồi thì cứ làm như bình thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Now we create a compound.}Giờ chúng ta sẽ chế tạo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Compounding is comparatively simple.\NWatch closely.}Nói chung là dễ. Nhìn cho kĩ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Take this, and first do this.}Làm thế này, thế này.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:32.62,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{TAK TAK TAK TAK TAK}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Then do this.}Rồi thế này.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:33.62,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{SWISH}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{And do this.}Và thế này.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:34.87,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{SIZZLE}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{And with this...}Rồi đây...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:39.87,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{BAM}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's done.}Xong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's not easy at all!}{\i0}Xong cái quái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Got it.}Hiểu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You've got to be lying!}Mày đừng có xạo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{No, really.}Không, thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Trust me, as long as it's not magic.}Tin tưởng anh đi. Miễn không phải ma thuật.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:51.14,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{TAK TAK TAK TAK TAK}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{First, take this, and then...}Đầu tiên, thế này, thế này...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:51.89,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{SWISH}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Do this...}Rồi thế này...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.14,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{SIZZLE}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Then this... And it's done.}Và thế này là xong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:57.64,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{BAM}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's totally not it!}{\i0}Mày đang làm cái gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{How did that end up as a cream puff?}{\i0}Thế quái nào lại thành bánh su kem?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You're screwing around, aren't you?}Ngươi đang giỡn mặt à?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm not screwing around.}Tớ không có giỡn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You start like this.}Đầu tiên làm thế này.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{'Kay.}Rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Then you add this.}Tiếp theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{'Kay.}Rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Stir well.}Trộn kĩ vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{'Kay.}Dễ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Add this last.}Thêm này vô.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{'Kay.}Xong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Okay.}Tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{BA-YUMMY}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Why is this!?}{\i0}Cái đéo gì thế này?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I watched him from start to finish.}{\i0}Mình nhìn nó từ đầu đến cuối.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{When did it become a cream puff!?}{\i0}Tại sao lại thành thế này?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You’re completely useless\Nwhen not fighting, huh?}Trừ chiến đấu ra thì ngươi kém tất cả à?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Well, yeah.}À ừ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Why is he so confident?}{\i0}Sao nó tự tin vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh well. Let me warn you.}Để ta cảnh báo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I won't lose to you ever again.}Ta sẽ không bao giờ thua ngươi nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{There's a reason\NI need to join the Bureau of Magic.}Ta cần phải vào Cục Ma pháp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{And that is?}Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's none of your business.}Không liên quan đến ngươi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But you equaled me,\Nif not more, in combat.}Nhưng ngươi đã mạnh hơn ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I will not allow some nobody\Nto take your coins away from you.}Nên đừng có để mất xu bạc vào tay kẻ khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You don't have to warn me,\Nbecause it won't happen.}Không cần phải dặn. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Quick with the comebacks.}Đừng có chỉ nói mồm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Let's try this again.}Làm lại thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{'Kay.}Rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{The all-dorm off-campus class\Nis coming up soon.}Chuẩn bị đến kì cắm trại chung rồi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I wonder if he'll be all right.}Thằng bé có ổn không đây...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{And then, that was when...}Và sau đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{No way. Are you serious?}Thật hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{And what happened after that?}Sau đó thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's when...}Sau đó á...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey, you bumped into me\Njust now, didn't you?}Này, mày vừa tông trúng tao đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Don't be walkin' into people's faces!}Đừng có lao thẳng vào ngườ khác chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey, hey, hey, hey!}Này này này này!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What am I supposed to do\Nif I'm not walkin' into people's faces?}Tao thích thế đấy, thì làm sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Side characters have no right\Nto give me orders, you moron!}Lũ nhân vật phụ thì đừng có mà lên tiếng!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{The Divine Visionaries are the ones\Nwho mold this world.}Những người được chọn là những kẻ điều khiển thế giới.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{They rule it.}Họ thống trị nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Tell me, what traits\Nshould a ruler possess?}Một kẻ thống trị là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{A noble bloodline and overwhelming power\Nthat brooks no argument.}Mang dòng máu cao quý và sức mạnh áp đảo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Correct.\NWhich means it is not those in Adler.}Chính xác. Tức là không phải lũ ở Adler.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It is us... Lang.}Mà là chúng ta... Lang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Seize all of their coins.}Cướp hết xu của chúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yessir.}Rõ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Nummy.}Ngon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Ugh, it's tasty? That's a mandragora!}Ngon á? Là Mandragora đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yum, yum.}Ừm ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Seriously!?}Thật hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Apparently, mandragora cream puffs are tasty.}{\i0}Có vẻ bánh su mandragora khá ngon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{And now, the next day...}{\i0}Giờ thì qua ngày tiếp theo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{We're supposed to be\Nhaving class here today.}Nghe bảo có tiết học ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What are we going to do here?}Cơ mà ở đây thì học gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What do you do in a forest...\NCamping?}Học trong rừng... cắm trại à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's for leisure. This is a magic school.}Cái đó là đi dã ngoại. Đây là trường học.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm number one!}Tao là số 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm number one!}Tao là số 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I, Dot Barrett,\Nis the main character of this world!}Tao, Dot Barrett, nhân vật chính!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{The world revolves around me!}Thế giới xoay quanh tao!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:25.18,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{DOT BARRETT}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Whew! It's revolving a bit more than—}Tao là người nổi tiếng nhất--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Whaddaya think you're looking at!?}Bọn mày nhìn cái gì hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Wierdo.}Thằng lập dị.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{A first-year from our dorm.}Cùng năm nhất.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Wait, it’s you! The Mushroom Head\Npeople keep talking about!}Khoan, mày là thằng đầu nấm đang nổi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You look like a side character to me.}Khác gì thằng nhân vật phụ không.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Who is this guy?}Thằng nào đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{As of today, you’re a side character\Nin both name and reality!}Kể từ hôm nay, mày sẽ là nhân vật phụ!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Because yours truly is—}Vì tao chính là--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mash!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Outdoor class is a bit scary.}Giờ học ngoại khoá hôm nay sợ quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm not going to push myself too hard.\NSo Mash, please take care out there, okay?}Tớ không định cố gắng quá sức đâu.\N Cậu cũng cẩn thận đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Thanks.}Cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Mash, could I possibly tag along—}Mash, liệu tớ có thể đi cùng cậu--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey.}Này.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:05.35,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{PFFT}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'll kill 'im!}Giết.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:11.98,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{CLENCH}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I friggin' hate guys\Nwho get attention from women!}Tao rất ghét những thằng hút gái!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'll kill you! I'll triple kill ya!}Tao sẽ giết! Giết mày 3 lần!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's ridiculous to begin with!}Thật quá là kì lạ!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{The global ratio of men to women\Nis supposed to be equal!}Tỷ lệ nam nữ là 1:1!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:28.50,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an7}{MEN}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:28.50,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an9}{WOMEN}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{So why isn't there a single girl\Nfalling in love with me!?}Vậy mà tại sao không em nào yêu tao?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's right, the answer is simple.}Câu trả lời quá đơn giản.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's because chumps like you\Nruin the system!}Vì loại như mày đang làm mất cân bằng!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:40.01,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{OOOOOOOOOO}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Guys like you are why we have\Nan aging population and a lower birthrate!}Chính bọn mày đã gây ra dân số già!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Won't someone just settle for me!?}Không ai nghĩ cho tao hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's why I made up my mind!}Thế nên tao đã tự nghĩ luôn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:42.01,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{BAM}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna join the Bureau of Magic\Nand rid this world of hot guys!}Tao sẽ vào Cục Pháp thuật và thoát khỏi lũ đẹp mã!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{- Oh Mash, I'll totally marry you.\N- Do cream puffs count as snacks?}Mash ơi, mình cưới nhau đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{That mandragora cream puff\Nwas tasty, huh?}Món su kem mandragora đó ngon ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Listen to me!}Nghe tao nói đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{My ego gets bruised the most\Nwhen I'm ignored!}Cái tôi của tao sẽ tổn thương lắm đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Quiet, all of you.}Im lặng hết.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Both Adler and Lang will participate\Nin this outdoor exercise.}Lần này hai nhà Lang và Adler sẽ cùng tham gia tiết học.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Your reward will be either a bronze or silver coin.\NBrace yourselves.}Phần thưởng sẽ là xu đồng hoặc xu bạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Your task is the extermination\Nof forest scorpions.}Nhiệm vụ là tiêu diệt bọ cạp rừng.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Bring me the stones\Nembedded in their foreheads.}Mang những viên đá trên trán chúng nộp cho thầy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Most forest scorpions\Nwill only earn you bronze coins,}Mỗi con sẽ cho ra 1 xu đồng.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{but a few are strong enough\Nto be worth silver coins.}Nhưng vài con đủ mạnh để có xu bạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You can identify them easily.}Các em có thể nhận biết chúng dễ dàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{If the stone in their foreheads\Nare square, they're worth silvers.}Nếu viên đá trên trán chúng hình vuông, là xu bạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Ordinary magic users\Nalmost certainly don't stand a chance.}Cơ mà ma pháp sư bình thường\N không đủ sức đấu với nó đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But such accomplishments\Nmake you Easton students.}Nhưng đây là học viện Ma thuật Easton.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Do what you must to survive.}Cố gắng sống sót.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{In you go, in order now.}Giờ thì vào rừng đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yeah, it's on!\NNo way I'm losing to you!}Ngon! Tao không thua mày đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'd like to make sure to get silver coins here.}Nhất định ta sẽ lấy được xu bạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I should do my best, too.}Tớ cũng sẽ cố hết sức.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You think you're hot stuff, right?}Mày đang ra vẻ tự mãn à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I can tell.}Tao hiểu rõ lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You think you're so special.}Mày nghĩ bản thân đặc biệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You mistakenly think\Nyou're not like the others.}Mày tưởng mình khác biệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You subconsciously\Nlook down on others, don't you?}Mày coi thường kẻ khác phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey, what are you doing over there?}Này, em làm gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'll mark you down for that.}Thầy cho rớt đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Sorry, Professor.\NWe were just horsing around.}Em xin lỗi. Chỉ đang nói chuyện xíu thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Right, first-year?}Phải không, năm 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yes, yes. That's the look.}Phải rồi, ánh mắt đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I want to make\Na pathetically messed up face outta you.}Tao sẽ dần cho mày một trận ra bã.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Looking forward to it, first-year!}Mong chờ lắm đó, năm 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey, Mash.}Này Mash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Ignore him.}Bỏ qua đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{He's one year older than us.}Tên đó lớn hơn 1 tuổi đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{And he's infamous for misconduct.}Và khá là nguy hiểm đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{He's injured multiple teachers\Nand students he doesn't like,}Hắn đã làm bị thương giáo\N viên và học sinh mà mình ghét.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{to the point of being held back a grade.}Đến mức bị đúp năm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But they consider his talent as a magic user,\Nso they haven't expelled him yet.}Nhưng do tài năng ma thuật nên không ai đuổi hắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You hear stuff like that often\Nfrom Lang dorm.}Mấy tên đó ở nhà Lang đầy rẫy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{So, don't bother with them.}Nên đừng dính dáng đến chúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm glad.}May quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I thought he crushed my cream puff.}Tưởng hắn đạp trúng bánh su kem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's why he made that face?}{\i0}Nó cay chỉ vì cái bánh su à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{And don't tuck food in there directly.\NIt's unhygienic.}Và đừng có nhét đồ ăn vào áo nữa. Dơ lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.09,0:14:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{'Kay.}Rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I smell tremendous danger.}Có mùi nguy hiểm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I think it's wiser for us to work as a pair.}Chúng ta nên hành động theo nhóm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Leave it to me, the oldest son...}Cứ để ta, kẻ từng làm anh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I zoned out, and now I'm all alone.}Vừa mới thẩn thơ là lạc luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh well.}Kệ đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Yo yo yo, get those tails on out,\Ndamned scorpions!}Nào nào nào, lũ bọ cạp chết tiệt!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna show up that mushroom head—}Nhất định phải vượt qua thằng đầu nấm--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Shut up.}Im mồm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:04.63,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{SLAP}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Just now, I wasted calories because of you.}Đừng để anh đây phải tốn calo vì chú.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{This is just terrible.}Thật phiền phức.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'll kill 'im.}Phải giết.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Fine. Forget about our class.}Dẹp vụ bọ cạp đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Right here right now, you're...}Ngay bây giờ, tao và mày...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Stop it!}Dừng lại đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Shut up!}Im!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Because of you, I...}Vì mày mà tao...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'll make you regret it!}Mày sẽ phải hối hận!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{S-Someone... Someone help me!}A-Ai đó... cứu tôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Explomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Raising your hand against a girl...\NYou're so done as a guy.}Ra tay với phụ nữ? Mày có còn là đàn ông không?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{U-Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:58.18,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{GLOW}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Thank you so much.}Cảm ơn bạn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{S-S-S-So beautiful!}{\i0}Đ-Đ-Đẹp quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Nope. Play it cool!\NI have to stay calm and act natural!}{\i0}Không, bình tĩnh! Phải tỏ ra ngầu lòi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That was nothing at...}Không có gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.07,0:16:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{H-H-Her hands... So soft...}{\i0}T-T-Tay mềm quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You're... so strong.}Cậu... thật mạnh mẽ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:23.58,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{GLOW}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Argh! I can't do it!}Không chịu nổi rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Now, is it almost time?}Sắp đến lúc rồi nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:44.31,Default,On-screen Text,0,0,0,,{\an8}{NOM NOM NOM}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Thank you so much for what you did earlier.}Cảm ơn cậu vì chuyện khi nãy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I-It was nothing.}K-Không có gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{O-O-Our knees are touching!}{\i0}Đ-Đầu gối đang chạm vào nhau!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So, this is the natural distance\Nof a modern couple?}{\i0}Hoá ra đây là khoảng cách thần thánh của các cặp đôi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:17:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Stay calm. Be still, my heart.}{\i0}Bình tĩnh nào trái tim tôi ơi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If I act weird, she'll catch on\Nthat I'm unpopular with girls.}{\i0}Nếu làm gì kì lạ, em ấy sẽ nhận ra mất.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Keep cool. Come on, me. Keep cool.}{\i0}Bình tĩnh. Tỏ ra ngầu nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Cool! Cool! Cool!}Ngầu ngầu ngầu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{What's with him? Freaky.}Nó bị gì vậy? Tởm quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Huh? What'd you just say?}Hả? Cậu vừa nói gì ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I was marveling at how\Nmanly and wonderful you are.}Tớ nghe nói cậu rất ra dáng đàn ông.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh no, I actually said wonderful.}Ý tớ là tuyệt vời đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Huh? I thought I heard two syllables.}Hả? Nhưng tôi nghe ra hai từ lận...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's the truth.}Tớ nói thật đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You really are wonderful.}Cậu đúng là thật tuyệt vời.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{With my magic, I can make anyone\Neven slightly attracted to me fall in love.}{\i0}Với Ma thuật của mình, tên nào cũng sẽ dính bùa yêu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{He's completely fallen for me now.}{\i0}Giờ thì hắn đã đổ mình hoàn toàn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Though, maybe he might\Nhave fallen even without magic.}{\i0}Cơ mà có khi không cần dùng ma thuật cũng tự đổ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Next up, that mushroom head...}{\i0}Giờ thì tên đầu nấm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Thank you too, kind sir.\NYou were a great help.}Cảm ơn cậu nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh, I didn't do anything.}Tôi có làm gì đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What? That's impossible.}{\i0}Cái gì? Không thể nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{There's never been a man\Nwho hasn't fallen under my spell.}{\i0}Làm gì có tên đàn ông nào chịu được bùa mê của chị?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{More like, any guy should be like “hurray!”\Nif a cute girl like me was flirting with him.}{\i0}Cơ mà thằng trai tân nào cũng phải đổ chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'll have to put more magic energy into it.}{\i0}Phải tăng cường ma thuật.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{That's not true.}Không có đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:18.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You really helped me out.}Cậu giúp đỡ tớ nhiều lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You're very wonderful.}Cậu rất tuyệt đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Sound, sight, touch.\NMy charm reaches all the senses!}{\i0}Âm thanh, thị giác, xúc giác. Tất cả đều được gia tăng!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{There is no man who can resist this!}{\i0}Làm gì ai chống lại nổi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I said, I didn't do anything.}Đã bảo là không làm gì rồi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's not working at all!?\NWhat is wrong with this guy?}{\i0}Hoàn toàn không ảnh hưởng? Tên này bị gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Does he seriously\Nnot find me attractive!? Die!}{\i0}Mình hoàn toàn không quyến rũ được hắn sao? Chết đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Fine. It's ours for the taking\Nnow that I have one of theirs.}{\i0}Thôi. Được 1 tên là đủ rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But you really did save me.}Nhưng đúng là cảm ơn cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Such a delicate facial expression.}{\i0}Nét mặt thật thanh tú.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Do you have some kind of circumstance?\NI'll lend an ear.}Cậu có nỗi lo gì à? Kể tôi nghe xem?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Actually, there’s a certain boy\Nthreatening me.}Thực ra... có một kẻ đang đe doạ tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{A certain boy?}Một kẻ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{A second-year by the name of Silva.}Một tên năm 2 tên là Silva.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{He's someone I don't hear\Nmany good things about.}Tớ nghe nói hắn không tốt lành gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{He's trying to take advantage\Nof magic only I can use.}Hắn đang cố gắng lợi dụng ma thuật của tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{He's been stalking me for all this time.}Và đã luôn bám theo tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I don't want to be involved\Nin anything that’s bad.}Tớ không muốn phải làm chuyện xấu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But he's forcing me to, like he did earlier.}Nhưng hắn cứ ép tớ phải làm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I don't know what I should do.}Tớ không biết phải làm sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry to bring this up so suddenly.}Xin lỗi vì tự nhiên...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{It's all right.\NI'm totally gonna beat that guy up.}Không sao. Tôi sẽ xử lý hắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oh no.\NPlease don't go out of your way.}Không... Đừng cố quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{No. He's definitely\Ngetting beaten to a pulp.}Không, tôi sẽ nghiền nát hắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Kind sir...}Cậu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Who's gonna beat who to a pulp?}Thằng nào đòi đánh tao?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{So you're the guy...}Vậy ra là mày...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'll be the one to kill you.}Tao sẽ nghiền nát mày!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You look like the cringiest punk out there.}Trông mày y như thằng đầu đường xó chợ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Whenever I come across a deluded loser\Nlike you, I can't help but give them a dose of reality.}Tao khoái gặp mấy thằng ảo tưởng lắm, \Nđể tao cho nó biết hiện thực tàn khốc.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{And when I do, what kind of look\Nwill you have on your face?}Và khi làm thế, nó sẽ thể hiện cho\N tao thấy bộ mặt như nào nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Explomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Machine Gun Explomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{I'm not done yet!}Chưa xong đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Oi oi oi oi!}Này này này!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Explomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Die twice!}Chết 2 lần đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Meanwhile...}{\i0}Trong khi đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{- I'm so glad you’re with us.\N- I’m so scared!}May quá! \N Cảm ơn cậu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Let go.}Thả ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Don't leave us!}Đừng bỏ bọn tớ mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Anyway, is he doing all right?}{\i0}Cơ mà nó có ổn không nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{- Please don't! No! Don't leave us!\N- You’re the only one we can rely on!}Làm ơn cứu bọn tớ!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It seems that second-year\Nwas targeting him.}{\i0}Có vẻ tên đúp lớp đang nhắm vào nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:17.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}{They haven’t run into each other, have they?}{\i0}Hi vọng đừng đụng độ nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Heh! You weren't much of anything!}Chả có gì mạnh cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Your puny magic\Ncan't break through mine.}Phép thuật của mày không làm gì được tao đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Got it!?}Hiểu chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Hey hey, what's wrong now?\NWhere'd all that energy go?}Này này! Sao thế? Khi nãy to mồm lắm mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.45,0:21:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{You're gonna kill me, right?}Mày đòi giết tao mà?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Why don't you try a bit harder?}Sao không cố gắng hơn đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{But it's no wonder!}Cơ mà cũng không nổi đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{Because even a moron can tell\Nthe difference...}Vì thằng ngu nhìn vào cũng biết...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.12,0:21:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{once they've seen the difference\Nin our skills!}thực lực của tao và mày khác nhau hoàn toàn.
